page.title: 01THE HIGH WYCOMBE AREA
page.content: OUR AREA IS MAINLY{MARLOW BOTTOM}AND THE{CRESSEX}AND{HANDY CROSS}AREAS OF {HIGH WYCOMBE.}THE LAND IS MOSTLY {RURAL},CONSISTING OF ARABLE AND DAIRY FARMS AND WOODLAND.THERE IS ALSO A LARGE{INDUSTRIAL}ESTATE.THE {RESIDENTIAL}AREAS INCLUDE BOTH MODERN AND TRADITIONAL ARCHITECTURAL STYLES. HIGH WYCOMBE IS SITUATED IN THE {CHILTERNS}AREA AND OUR SURROUNDINGS ARE PREDOMINANTLY LIMESTONE HILLS AND WIDE VALLEYS.THERE IS AN IMPORTANT INTERSECTION OF THE{M40}MOTORWAY WHICH CONNECTS{OXFORD}AND{LONDON}. THE OUTSTANDING SCENERY AND OUR PROXIMITY TO LONDON AND OXFORD ATTRACT MANY TOURISTS TO OUR AREA.
